{"type":null,"faqId":7111,"title":"如何节省手机所使用的流量？","answer":"1.不使用数据业务时，请关闭手机的数据业务开关；<br />2.在有Wifi网络可以使用的环境中，请使用Wifi连接；<br />3.登录wap网站比登录www网站更节省流量。<br />关闭数据业务：进入<strong>主菜单</strong>-&gt;<strong>设置</strong>-&gt;<strong>无线和网络</strong>-&gt;<strong>移动网络</strong>-&gt;<strong>取消勾选已启用数据或者在通知栏中关闭数据开关</strong>；<br />关闭后台数据同步：进入<strong>主菜单</strong>-&gt;<strong>设置</strong>-&gt;<strong>帐户与同步</strong>-&gt;<strong>取消勾选背景数据/自动同步</strong>。","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7251","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1313738397000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":898,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":17,"times":5,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":3.4,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}